The paper discusses reinforcement learning algorithms and their application to autonomous driving, which suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories. The use of deep learning and optimization techniques in the proposed algorithm suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The focus on decision-making and control tasks in autonomous driving suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The use of computer vision in the autonomous driving tasks suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the focus on safety-critical systems suggests that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
